front.title: •Corporal Vandolay
front.gametext: May use 1 Force to search your Reserve Deck and take one Spice Mines Of Kessel or Detention Block Corridor into hand. Shuffle, cut and replace. While at a mobile site, We Have A Prisoner is a Used Interrupt.
front.lore: ISB attache to the Executor. Detention Officer. Political Liaison for COMPNOR. Responsible for all prisoner transfers. Fiercely loyal to the Emperor's New Order.
